@startuml
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class "onlycomplete" {
    display only complete button has been clicked
    display only the complete to-do lists
}

class "saveAll" {
    save All button has been clicked
    save all the to-do lists
}

class "main" {
    display only complete button
    save all button
    save button
    open X button
    open All button
}

class "openX" {
    open X button has been clicked
    open the to-do list you pick
}

class "openAll" {
    open All button has been clicked
    open all the to-do list
}

class "save" {
    save button has been clicked
    save the current to-do lists
}


' Relationships from main to other classes using generalization arrows pointing towards 'main'. 
note right of main : This represents inheritance or implementation relationships where \nthe child elements inherit behavior/structure defined in parent(main). 

onlycomplete --|> main  
saveAll --|> main   
save --|^ main    
openAll --|> main     
openX --|> main  

@enduml
